# Blog Content

- File naming: `YYYY-MM-DD_slug.md` in `src/content/blog/{en,es}/`
- Required frontmatter: `title`, `date` (YYYY-MM-DD), `excerpt` (max 160 chars), `tags` (array)
- Optional frontmatter: `author`, `image`
- Tags reference IDs from `src/content/tags/`: `tracks`, `tools`, `logistics`, `community`
- Each post must have a corresponding post in the other locale directory
- Tag files have `name_es`, `name_en`, `description`, and `order` fields
